'''羅倫佐·麥可·墨菲·奧登'''（Lorenzo Michael Murphy Odone，{{bd|1978年|5月29日|2008年|5月30日|catIdx=O}}），是罕見疾病[[腎上腺腦白質失養症|腎上腺腦白質失養症]]（ALD）的患者。其父母[[奧古斯都·奧登|奧古斯都·奧登]]與[[米謝拉·奧登|米謝拉·奧登]]為羅倫佐研發出飲用[[三油酸甘油酯|三油酸甘油酯]]（glycerol trioleate）與[[三芥子酸甘油脂|三芥子酸甘油脂]]（glycerol trierucate）的混合油的療法，這種油後來便稱為「[[羅倫佐的油|羅倫佐的油]]」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2062622/Obituary-Lorenzo-Odone.html|title=Lorenzo Odone Subject of Lorenzo's Oil, the film portraying his parents' quest to cure his degenerative disease|date=1 Jun 2008|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=14 June 2010|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226220641/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2062622/Obituary-Lorenzo-Odone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並有一部同名[[電影|電影]]《[[羅倫佐的油_(電影)|羅倫佐的油]]》來描述羅倫佐的故事<ref>{{cite web | title=About Lorenzo, his Parents, and Oumouri | work=The Myelin Project | url=http://www.myelin.org/en/cms/?15 | accessdate=2010-01-02 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080903102051/http://www.myelin.org/en/cms/?15 | archivedate=2008-09-03 }}</ref> 。

羅倫佐·奧登在他三十歲生日的隔天，因侵入性[[肺炎|肺炎]]於[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]的家中逝世<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2062622/Obituary-Lorenzo-Odone.html|title=Obituaries: Lorenzo Odone|date=1 Jun 2008|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=5 September 2011|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226220641/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2062622/Obituary-Lorenzo-Odone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

